{"title":"大伙房水库短歌","authors":["李振哲","李代生"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":11,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大伙房水库短歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李振哲  李代生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天高，白云飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微风吹动杨柳梢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水库湖面客轮跑；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊出鲤鱼吐白泡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片湖水泛银波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艘艘汽艇上面飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声声汽笛唱新歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水库连成幸福道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着浪花翻思潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪水卷过房屋倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"良田一片黄沙地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灾民露宿在荒郊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水库建成贮清水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清水灌田浇稻苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机轮搅水发了电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银灯照亮荒山坳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天高，红旗飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青山绿水都含笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐着看，站着瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着水库又笑了。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}